# Faberon agents

Before changing code in this repository:

1. Read `AGENTS.md` and `CONSTITUTION.md` at the repository root.
2. Read the complete `SKILL.md` for every applicable skill listed in `AGENTS.md`.
3. Run package-manager, lint, test, and build commands only from the affected app directory (`frontend`, `backend`, or `mobile`).

Skills under `skills/` are canonical. Entries under `.cursor/skills/` only point to them.
